Job Details
Required Sales Manager for Cargo Handling and Clearance. Applicants should have min of 5 years of working experience as commercial manager in same industry. Candidates Should have experience  in  cargoes, Brokering, Projects & Semi Liner sales and in dealing with Shipping carriers. Should be capable of taking of new challenges. Self oriented.Fluent in English. Must Poses Computer skills for Microsoft Office.
Requirements
Skills: Sales, Marketing, Business Developmen, Warehouse, Logistics, Cargo.
Ensure increased coverage of the market and build up potential clients for an enhanced long-term business relationship.
